 2002-18232002-10-240,  ,  IA&ND,  , 
PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the SAULTEAUX BAND, of the mines and minerals existing within, upon or under (a) some 259 hectares of land situated in Saskatchewan, as an addition to Saulteaux Indian Reserve No. 159, and (b) existing within, upon or under another three hectares of land, as an addition to its Reserve No. 159B.
